physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Dysmorphic facial features (hypertelorism, microphthalmia, mongoloid palpebral fissures, microretrognathia, long philtrum), membranous partial cleft palate, low-set ears, prominent occiput, umbilical and inguinal hernia, syndactyly of the third and fourth digits of the feet, fifth digit clinodactyly, floating testicles, axial hypotonia, and limb hypertonia.
